19:44.280 --> 19:48.700
<b>Please be at ease.
Mash is doing well at school.</b>

19:49.910 --> 19:52.500
<b>This isn't much,
but please have some herbal tea.</b>

19:52.500 --> 19:53.710
<b>Oh, thank you.</b>

19:53.710 --> 19:56.170
<b>That's so not like you.</b>

19:56.460 --> 19:58.090
<b>I have something for you, too.</b>

19:59.130 --> 20:00.840
<b>- Please have some merch.
- Of who?</b>

20:00.970 --> 20:01.840
<b>My little sister.</b>

20:01.840 --> 20:03.010
<b>Why!?</b>

20:03.640 --> 20:07.640
<b>He doesn't understand that everyone
has different priorities.</b>

20:07.640 --> 20:09.350
<b>I-I see.</b>

20:14.060 --> 20:19.610
<b>They're quite unique. All of them.</b>

20:19.610 --> 20:21.280
<b>Yes, they are.</b>

20:21.860 --> 20:23.820
<b>You must have a hard time.</b>

20:23.820 --> 20:24.990
<b>Yes.</b>

20:25.780 --> 20:26.620
<b>But...</b>

20:28.540 --> 20:33.250
<b>I was never able to let Mash
go outside until now.</b>

20:33.960 --> 20:38.000
<b>I never dreamed he'd be surrounded
by such wonderful friends.</b>

20:40.630 --> 20:43.800
<b>I hope it lasts forever.</b>

20:45.430 --> 20:46.760
<b>I'm sure...</b>

20:47.220 --> 20:49.560
<b>I'm sure it will.</b>

20:53.020 --> 20:55.690
<b>Hope they won't mind us barging in.</b>

20:56.020 --> 20:59.150
<b>To defeat Abel
so soundly without magic.</b>

20:59.150 --> 21:01.990
<b>You think I can let
someone like that slide?</b>

21:02.650 --> 21:06.160
<b>Hey, what was that boy's name?</b>

21:06.370 --> 21:07.530
<b>Mash.</b>

21:07.530 --> 21:09.200
